( 1 ) The Community reserves the right to amend the arrangements for petroleum products of 27.10 , 27.11 , 27.12 , ex 27.13 ( paraffin , petroleum wax , wax derived from bituminous minerals , paraffin residues ) and 27.14 of the Brussels tariff scheme upon adoption of a common definition of origin for petroleum products , decisions under the common commercial policy for the products concerned or the introduction of a common energy policy .
