In order to implement the Agreement referred to in Article 1 , the Principality of Liechtenstein may , without changing its nature as a bilateral agreement between the Community and Switzerland , exercise its interests through a representative in the framework of the Swiss delegation to the Joint Committee .

This Supplementary Agreement shall be approved by Switzerland , the Principality of Liechtenstein and the Community in accordance with their own procedures and shall enter into force simultaneously with the Agreement referred to in Article 1 and shall remain in force for as long as the Treaty of 29 June 2006 .
