( 2 ) They shall also take all necessary measures to ensure that these substances reach the recipients referred to in Article 3 of this Convention quickly and as quickly as possible .

The Contracting Parties , through the Secretary @-@ General of the Council of Europe , shall submit to each other a list of national and / or regional reference laboratories authorised to issue the certificate provided for in Article 4 and to distribute the reagents introduced for tissue typing .

