Article 40
The Supplementary Agreements shall enter into force simultaneously with or as soon as possible after the entry into force of this Convention . The Organisation , the Community and the States shall make every effort to ensure that these Agreements enter into force within ninety days of the entry into force of this Convention ; an extension of this period shall require agreement between the Organisation , the Community and the States .
