Article 41
On the basis of the initial report referred to in Article 62 , the Organisation shall draw up a summary inventory of all nuclear material subject to safeguard measures in States , irrespective of its origin , and shall continue to maintain this inventory on the basis of subsequent reports and the results of its inspections .
